name: Weeding
description: Your wedding is one of the most special, important and memorable days of your life. Weddings are more than just a union of two people, it is a reunion of friends, family and life-long memories. Our goal is to make your wedding day relaxed and enjoyable for everyone. Your wedding day is filled with breathtaking moments and many emotions, but the big day is notorious for flying by! As your wedding photographers, our job is to capture all the special, heart-warming moments so you will be able to easily reflect on every special detail of your wedding day for the rest of your life. We will provide you with beautiful documentation of your wedding day that will last a lifetime. We will capture wedding portraits of the bride and groom, the wedding party, the families, the guests and all the details and special moments that make the wedding so memorable

name: Engagement
description: If you have recently become engaged, it’s time to start planning for the big day.First of all, from A&C Photography: congratulations on your engagement! Planning a wedding is bound to be one of the most exciting and fun parts of your life. Part of this should include planning your engagement photography session. Your session is a great chance to get comfortable with your chosen wedding photographer, as well as a chance to get some fantastic pictures for your “save the date” cards!After your engagement session, we will schedule a time and date to go over all of your fun and romantic photos. We can use this time to go over details for your wedding, choose your favorite shots, and discuss various packages for prints and digital copies.See our options for engagement photography sessions below.

name: Event Photography
description: Over the years we have covered many different types of events. Our Silly Studio photo booth rental is a very popular feature at company events, birthday parties, bar and bat mitzvahs and weddings. We have covered fundraising events for non-profit organizations, such as Walk with Sally, and also political events that raise money for certain causes. We have taken photographs at school dances and other school-wide events. We covered a three day event for Mentor Graphics that included multiple awards ceremonies and a banquet dinner with over 3,000 attendees. For the past six years we have covered Living Spaces’ company picnic and holiday party.
